title: Samsung Galaxy Tab S2 8.0 Unboxing & First Impressions
description:
The new Galaxy Tab S2 is so ridiculously thin and light, it makes the iPad Mini feel fat. Along with great design and incredible Super AMOLED screen, there's a lot to get excited about with Samsungs latest tablet Galaxy Tab. 

This is my unboxing and first impressions video - there will be a full review coming very soon!

Don't forget to like & subscribe! Thanks!
